 Some factors that were considered in pervious studies for electricity price forecasting can be summed as follows [4]:


•
Time: Hour of the day, day of the week, month, year and special days;


•
Reserve: Historical and forecasted reserve;


•
Price: Historical price;


•
Load: Historical and forecasted loads.

